data.title: Valencia College
data.text:
President's and Dean's Lists

Valencia College publishes both President’s and Dean’s Honor Lists each term in recognition of high scholastic achievement. These achievements will appear on your Valencia College transcript as part of your academic record for each term of recognition. Academic honors are earned at the end of each term if you have completed successfully at least six college credits (including developmental courses) and have no grades of F, I, M, W, or WN.
